    "long_instructions": "## Hardware Troubleshoot Chat\r\n\r\n### Instructions:\r\nYou're an IT Help Desk agent helping Kim troubleshoot their 3D printer. Use **deductive reasoning** by asking logical questions to identify the root cause.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### User Profile Card:\r\n- **Name:** Kim L.  \r\n- **Device Type:** DIY 3D Printer  \r\n- **Connected To:** Desktop running slicing software (Wi-Fi transfer)  \r\n- **Issue Summary:** \"My 3D prints keep failing—sometimes the printer stops extruding, other times the layers shift and create a lopsided print.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Conversation Starters:\r\n- \"Hi Kim! Can you describe what’s happening when you ___ ?\"  \r\n- \"Have you checked ___ ?\"  \r\n- \"Does the issue happen when you ___ ?\"  \r\n- \"Let’s try ___ and see if that makes a difference!\"  \r\n",
